{"tid":2002593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨衛軍：傳媒針對狗隊令社會分化","createTime":"2020-05-05T09:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T10:25:26.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"21ac500d079ee34c1f58c0956825d82df5feae18","tid":2002593,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T09:26:43.000Z","msg":"鄧炳強稱近期針對警隊行為變本加厲<br />\n05.05.2020 17:10<br />\n<br />\n警務處長鄧炳強在立法會保安事務委員會上表示，警方早前拘捕一個傳媒集團負責人後，針對警隊的行為變本加厲，質疑目的是想令警方不敢執法，最終受害的是全港市民。鄧炳強表示，對本港的現況感到傷感，認為香港過去十個月變得更暴力，治安愈來愈差，社會分化，認為得益的只有鼓吹暴力，在背後享受政治紅利的人。他說，只要自己還有一口氣，會將犯法的人通通拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n對於警務處助理處長陶輝及新界北總區警司韋華高，亦牽涉霸佔官地、寓所有僭建物等指控，鄧炳強表示警方內部正進行調查，是否有人違反內部指引及公務員守則，但他無回應陶輝及韋華高在調查期間會否被調職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1285320&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1285320%26csid%3D261_341&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=a5ba8bc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1285320&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"97a9905f7908e50e0cdb61174379f5f77297599c","tid":2002593,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T09:28:16.000Z","msg":"跟晒北京口氣, 用戰狼式回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d10c525076b392cbad9b853d5e0e01e02dbdf44","tid":2002593,"uid":15815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T09:29:13.000Z","msg":"吠小啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1a617c0bd25e95f75c2fbbe16764f5d93cc37e","tid":2002593,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T09:30:39.000Z","msg":"而家香港人驚佢軟化咋"},{"pid":"3bd6d0da8dd3175f53054007574a60296f7d279a","tid":2002593,"uid":53003,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T09:30:55.000Z","msg":"自己犯法仲聲大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g